If you have the 36,000 gp the single best item you can get is an orange
prism ioun stone (+1 caster level).  If you have to forgo everything
else to get it. do so, some of the other ioun stones are useful too.
Right behind that are metamagic rods.  I don't remember if they had
those in 3.0 though.

If you don't have that kind of money Pearls of power for any level you
tend to use up, probably 2nd level spells if you like to buff.  Wand(s)
of cure light wounds (if you don't have one or more already), scrolls,
wands, potions, or staves of anything else you might need to use
(scrolls for the rare contingencies, wands for the everyday backups).
Boots of speed perhaps if you fight toe to toe often.  Ring of blinking
is also a great defense.

